  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Weight &lt; 100 kg

          -  score UCLA &gt; 4

          -  prosthesis of first intention

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnant

          -  score UCLA &lt; 4

          -  osteotomy near to prosthesis

          -  prosthesis requiring an osseous transplant

          -  prosthesis already set up

          -  infections, contagious diseases (HIV, tuberculosis, hepatitis, venereal diseases) or
             metastasis

          -  neuromuscular diseases able to perturb walking or staying

          -  congenital or acquired disease, or previous surgery able to have consequences on
             results and prosthesis survey according to the surgeon
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
